data.description: Interest rate buydown option available.   Enjoy the evenings on the covered front porch or out back by the patio & firepit. Open & updated main level includes tile flooring throughout, elegant kitchen with granite counters, a bar area, oversized SS farm sink, built in cabinets for pantry storage, new SS appliances, breakfast nook with added charm of  bay window . Family Room features electric fireplace/heater. Use the front room as a dining room or more formal living room. Primary bedroom has updated bathroom w/tiled rain shower, floating vanity, modern free standing soaker tub plus built in orgnization in w/i closet. W/D located upstairs.
